section\" data-id=\"1bba3a1\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3a5d21a elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"3a5d21a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7be550b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7be550b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Just like that, you have created a page for your Independence Day website. Isn’t that amazing? Now all that’s left to do is add your own content, and customize the template to suit your personal style.</span></p><h3><b>Step 2: Customize Your 4th of July Website</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Customizing your 4th of July template is very easy to do and can be done in less than 5 minutes. Just click on any section that you want to customize and use the </span><b>Elementor Editor</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> on your left to style your website. Play around with the background colors, typography, and images until you have your own unique WordPress Independence Day website</span></p><p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-489467 aligncenter\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/C2X2Gwvgt1.gif\" alt=\"4th of July\" width=\"1920\" height=\"903\" /></p><h3><b>Step 3: Save Your Independence Day Website Design On MyCloud </b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Templately comes with a very useful feature that lets you</span> <a href=\"https://docs.templately.com/home/save-templates-design-on-mycloud/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b>save your design on MyCloud</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. With this option, you will be able to reuse your Independence Day website design later on, at any time from anywhere. All you have to do is right-click anywhere on your page and choose the option </span><b>‘Save Page in Templately’</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. </span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-34128db elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"34128db\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c88ab91 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"c88ab91\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-edff402 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"edff402\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1600\" height=\"779\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"4th of July\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190.png 1600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190-600x292.png 600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190-768x374.png 768w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1592292814190-1536x748.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" />											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b26ee87 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b26ee87\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-43be22c elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"43be22c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db6d685 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"db6d685\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Final Outcome</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74983d8 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"74983d8\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d7bba4 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"1d7bba4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-972a21f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"972a21f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Congratulations! By following these three simple steps, you’ve created your very own <strong>Independence Day website</strong> on WordPress using the ready-made <strong>July4</strong> template pack from <strong>Templately</strong>.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-489469 aligncenter\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/HGwX4ZhXri.gif\" alt=\"4th of July\" width=\"1892\" height=\"838\" /></span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">We hope you have found this tutorial very helpful, especially during these difficult times. If you have any problems, feel free to contact </span><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/support/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>our support team</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> for further assistance, or join our </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/essentialaddons/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b>Facebook Community</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> where you can connect with other WordPress experts and website designers.</span></p><p> </p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n		<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/independence-day-website/\">Instantly Create 4th of July Independence Day Website With Elementor Template</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net\">WPDeveloper</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/Commen