image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\" title=\\\"List of legal entity types by country\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/List_of_legal_entity_types_by_country\\\">business entities<\\/a>, whose aim is generating profit<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\\\">financial entities and&nbsp;<a style=\\\"color: #0b0080; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\" title=\\\"Bank\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Bank\\\">banks<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\\\">programs or educational organisations.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\\\">A company can be created as a legal person so that the company itself has&nbsp;<a style=\\\"color: #0b0080; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\" title=\\\"Limited liability\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Limited_liability\\\">limited liability<\\/a>&nbsp;as members perform or fail to discharge their duty according to the publicly declared&nbsp;<a style=\\\"color: #0b0080; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\" title=\\\"Incorporation (business)\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Incorporation_(business)\\\">incorporation<\\/a>, or published policy. When a company closes, it may need to be&nbsp;<a style=\\\"color: #0b0080; background-image: none; backgroun