e: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\" title=\\\"List of legal entity types by country\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/List_of_legal_entity_types_by_country\\\">business entities<\\/a>, whose aim is generating profit<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\\\">financial entities and\\u00a0<a style=\\\"color: #0b0080; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\" title=\\\"Bank\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Bank\\\">banks<\\/a><\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\\\">programs or educational organisations.<\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\\\">A company can be created as a legal person so that the company itself has\\u00a0<a style=\\\"color: #0b0080; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\" title=\\\"Limited liability\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Limited_liability\\\">limited liability<\\/a>\\u00a0as members perform or fail to discharge their duty according to the publicly declared\\u00a0<a style=\\\"color: #0b0080; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\" title=\\\"Incorporation (business)\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Incorporation_(business)\\\">incorporation<\\/a>, or published policy. When a company closes, it may need to be\\u00a0<a style=\\\"color: #0b0080; background-image: none; background-position: